OL,3,CScientists investigating 'alarming
OL,4,Crise' in a type of cancer affecting
OL,5,Cunder-50s
OL,7,FLondon scientists are investigating an
OL,8,F'alarming rise' in a type of cancer
OL,9,Fthat mainly affects under-50s by
OL,10,Fteaming up with medical experts around
OL,11,Fthe world.
OL,13,FCases of bowel cancer appear to
OL,14,Fincrease with each new generation and
OL,15,Ffactors such as obesity and diet could
OL,16,Fadd to the risk, as well as
OL,17,Fenvironmental and social factors.
