OL,3,CScientists investigating 'alarming
OL,4,Crise' in a type of cancer affecting
OL,5,Cunder-50s
OL,7,F"We applied because colon cancer,
OL,8,Fparticularly in younger adults, is a
OL,9,Fgrowing problem. Our range of
OL,10,Fmultidisciplinary skills can play an
OL,11,Fimportant role, particularly with
OL,12,Fregards to nutrition and the gut
OL,13,Fmicrobiome.
OL,15,F"People with rare and early cancers
OL,16,Fdon't get as much research attention,
OL,17,Fso this is a key opportunity to better
OL,18,Funderstand the risk factors and how to
OL,19,Fimprove prevention."
